.TH ABRAFLEXI-MATCH-CASH 1 "July 17, 2026" "abraflexi-matcher" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
abraflexi-match-cash \- Match all capable issued invoices against incoming payments in AbraFlexi
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B abraflexi-match-cash
[OPTIONS]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B abraflexi-match-cash
matches unpaid issued invoices against incoming bank payments using
AbraFlexi's own bank-matching logic, without the day-range restriction
used by
.BR abraflexi-matcher-out (1).
It is a legacy variant kept for backward compatibility; for new
deployments prefer
.BR abraflexi-matcher-out (1)
or the single-method matchers
.BR abraflexi-match-varsym (1),
.BR abraflexi-match-specsym (1)
and
.BR abraflexi-match-accountno (1).
.SH OPTIONS
This script uses environment variables for configuration.
.TP
.B RESULT_FILE
Path to the output JSON report file.
.TP
.B MATCHER_LOCALIZE
Locale for log/report messages: en_US (default), cs_CZ, or sk_SK.
.SH ENVIRONMENT
The script requires AbraFlexi connection details:
.TP
.B ABRAFLEXI_URL
AbraFlexi server URL
.TP
.B ABRAFLEXI_LOGIN
AbraFlexi login username
.TP
.B ABRAFLEXI_PASSWORD
AbraFlexi password
.TP
.B ABRAFLEXI_COMPANY
AbraFlexi company code
.SH FILES
.TP
.I match_report.json
Default output file containing the matching results in JSON format compliant with the multiflexi report schema.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR abraflexi-matcher-out (1),
.BR abraflexi-match-bank (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Written by Vitex Software.
